325
00:16:41,350 --> 00:16:41,810
Well,

326
00:16:42,080 --> 00:16:42,610
don't worry.

327
00:16:43,110 --> 00:16:44,300
I won't abandon you.

328
00:16:44,800 --> 00:16:46,300
Get some rest. Don't be scared.

329
00:17:06,710 --> 00:17:07,850
