339
00:17:44,400 --> 00:17:45,010
Gelin.

340
00:17:46,230 --> 00:17:47,290
Do you have a crush on Ye Ye?

341
00:17:53,680 --> 00:17:54,450
You know?

342
00:17:55,960 --> 00:17:57,250
Back when you cried at the academy,

343
00:17:57,880 --> 00:17:58,820
