351
00:18:16,840 --> 00:18:17,940
But for all these years,

352
00:18:18,710 --> 00:18:19,290
Changyue,

353
00:18:19,640 --> 00:18:20,340
Ye,

354
00:18:20,710 --> 00:18:21,450
