362
00:18:40,510 --> 00:18:41,580
But today...

363
00:18:43,200 --> 00:18:44,490
Seeing them today,

364
00:18:45,340 --> 00:18:46,380
I realized

365
00:18:47,680 --> 00:18:49,660
