372
00:19:10,270 --> 00:19:11,180
You're right.

373
00:19:11,440 --> 00:19:12,580
It's good you have me.

374
00:19:12,790 --> 00:19:13,860
You won't be alone.

375
00:19:19,160 --> 00:19:21,200
