00:24:31,640 --> 00:24:32,340
Master?

453
00:24:34,960 --> 00:24:35,660
Xiaobangchui.

454
00:24:35,680 --> 00:24:36,770
You call this

455
00:24:36,790 --> 00:24:37,420
