475
00:25:21,400 --> 00:25:22,180
Xiaobangchui!

476
00:25:22,600 --> 00:25:23,770
Xiaobangchui!

477
00:25:23,920 --> 00:25:24,450
Run!

478
00:25:25,200 --> 00:25:25,970
